'''米歇尔·英格丽·威廉斯'''（{{lang-en|Michelle Ingrid Williams}}，{{bd|1980年|9月9日||}}），[[美國|美國]]女[[演員|演員]]、歌手。她于1990年代初在电视上出道，在1998年至2003年间凭借[[WB電視網|WB電視網]]青春剧《[[恋爱时代_(美国电视剧)|恋爱时代]]》中的{{le|简·林德利|Jen Lindley}}一角取得知名度。她也开始接拍长篇电影，包括《{{le|月光光心慌慌7|Halloween H20: 20 Years Later}}》（1998）、《{{le|迪克 (1999年电影)|Dick (film)|迪克}}》（1999）和《{{le|我的忧郁青春|Prozac Nation (film)}}》（2001）。

自2000年代起，威廉斯主要出现在独立剧情电影中，在影评界广受好评。2005年电影《[[断背山|断背山]]》是她职业生涯的高光作品之一，使她获得了[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|奥斯卡最佳女配角奖]]提名。她随后参演了《[[搖滾啟示錄|搖滾啟示錄]]》（2007）、《{{le|纽约提喻法|Synecdoche, New York}}》（2008）和[[马丁·斯科塞斯|马丁·斯科塞斯]]执导的《[[隔離島|隔離島]]》（2010）。威廉斯在2008年影片《{{le|温迪和露西|Wendy and Lucy}}》中的流浪者角色为她赢得了赞誉，她在《[[藍色情人節|藍色情人節]]》（2010）中与[[瑞恩·高斯林|瑞恩·高斯林]]演对手戏，获得了[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|奥斯卡最佳女主角奖]]提名。2011年，威廉斯在《[[我与梦露的一周|我与梦露的一周]]》中出演[[玛丽莲·梦露|玛丽莲·梦露]]，赢得了[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角|金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角奖]]，也获得了她的第三个奥斯卡奖提名。2017年再憑著《[[海邊的曼徹斯特|海邊的曼徹斯特]]》獲得奥斯卡最佳女配角奖提名。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
威廉斯出生于美国[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]的[[卡利斯佩爾_(蒙大拿州)|卡利斯佩爾]]。母亲卡拉·英格丽（{{lang|en|Carla Ingrid}}，娘家姓“斯文森”），是一位家庭主妇。父亲{{le|拉里·理查德·威廉斯|Larry R. Williams}}，是一位写手兼期货交易员，还两次竞选[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]][[美国参议院|参议员]]<ref name="ohw">{{cite book|last=Vitale|first=Sarah A.|title=Who's Who in California|publisher=Who's Who Historical Society|year=1992|page=349|isbn=1-880142-01-05|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.askmen.com/celebs/women/actress/34_michelle_williams.html |title=Michelle Williams |work=[[Askmen|Askmen]] |publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717161324/http://www.askmen.com/celebs/women/actress/34_michelle_williams.html |archivedate=2011-07-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/This-Day-in-History---September-9_7943379 |title=This Day in History – September 9 |work=[[The_Jamaica_Observer|The Jamaica Observer]] |date=2010-09-09 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118235039/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/This-Day-in-History---September-9_7943379 |archivedate=2012-01-18 }}</ref><ref name="mwilliams2">{{cite journal|title=Michelle Williams|journal=Maxim (online)|url=http://www.maxim.com/amg/girls/todays-girl/86465/michelle-williams.html|accessdate=2011-09-03|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130104011708/http://www.maxim.com/amg/girls/todays-girl/86465/michelle-williams.html|archivedate=2013-01-04}}</ref><ref name="mc126">{{citation |title=Belle Michelle |first=Leslie |last=Bennetts |work=[[Marie_Claire|Marie Claire]] |publisher=[[Hearst_Corporation|Hearst Corporation]] |date=February 2011 |page=126 |issue=08530 |accessdate=2011-07-08}}</ref>。她的父母分居，她有一个妹妹佩吉（{{lang|en|Paige}}）和三个异父或异母同胞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/9873244/Oz-the-Great-and-Powerful-Michelle-Williams-interview.html|title=Michelle Williams interview|publisher=telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2015-03-08|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001135039/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/9873244/Oz-the-Great-and-Powerful-Michelle-Williams-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="filmref">{{cite web | url = http://www.filmreference.com/film/36/Michelle-Williams.html | title = Michelle Williams Biography (1980-) | publisher = FilmReference.com | accessdate = 2013-01-16 | language = en | archive-date = 2020-04-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200423225838/http://www.filmreference.com/film/36/Michelle-Williams.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。威廉斯有挪威、英格兰、德国、丹麦、瑞士、瑞典、苏格兰和威尔士血统<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ethnicelebs.com/michelle-williams|title=Michelle Williams|work=Ethnic Celebs|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224035239/http://ethnicelebs.com/michelle-williams|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/michelle-williams|title=Michelle Williams|first=Vendela|last=Vida|work=[[Interview_(magazine)|Interview]]|date=May 2011|accessdate=2012-06-20|language=en|archive-date=2012-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120605182544/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/michelle-williams/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Michelle |first=Brooke Lee Poer |last=Trench |work=Madison Magazine |date=January 2011 |accessdate=2011-07-09}}</ref>。小时候的她孤僻不合群，她说：“我的确与父母保持距离，在一定程度上到现在也是如此……我发现自己这样过得不错。我不知道为什么。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"I was really secretive with my parents and I think I sort of continued that... I found that by keeping to myself I got on OK. I don't know why."}}|group="原文"}}”威廉斯九岁时，全家搬到加州[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|圣地亚哥]]。她在早年观看了当地剧团的《[[汤姆索亚历险记|汤姆索亚历险记]]》后开始对表演产生兴趣<ref name="thr2008">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-roundtable-actresses-124073 |title=Oscar Roundtable: The Actresses |publisher=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |date=2008-12-08 |first1=Stephen |last1=Galloway |first2=Elizabeth |last2=Guider |accessdate=2014-11-03 |language=en |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103040035/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-roundtable-actresses-124073 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 职业生涯 ===
==== 1990年代 ====
1990年代早期，威廉斯在《{{le|一步一步来|Step by Step (TV series)}}》、《{{le|男人唔易做|Home Improvement (TV series)}}》等电视节目中客串，开启了演艺生涯。1993年，她在电视剧《[[护滩使者|护滩使者]]》中出演了布里吉特·鲍尔斯（{{lang|en|Bridget Bowers}}）一角<ref name="Maytum">{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/step-by-step-1994#content |work=[[Total_Film|Total Film]] |publisher=Future Publishing |title=Step by Step (1994) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111054311/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/step-by-step-1994#content |dead-url=no }}|</ref><ref name ="Dearbhla">{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/baywatch-1993#content |work=[[Total_Film|Total Film]] |publisher=Future Publishing |title=Baywatch (1993) |first=Dearbhla |last=Coughlan |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2014-01-23 |language=en |archive-date=2014-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204011139/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/baywatch-1993#content |dead-url=no }}|</ref>。她在[[冒险片|冒险片]]《{{le|新灵犬莱西|Lassie (1994 film)}}》（1994）中初登大银幕<ref name="peoplebio1">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/michelle_williams/biography |title=Michelle Williams: Biography |work=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |publisher=Time Warner Inc |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2013-07-16 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I8yWoOym?url=http://www.people.com/people/michelle_williams/biography |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[科幻片|科幻片]]《[[异种|异种]]》（1995）中，她扮演了少女时期的女主角，该角色拥有外星人和人类结合的基因，成年时期的演员为[[娜塔莎·韓絲翠|娜塔莎·韓絲翠]]<ref name="Maytum"/>。随后，她出现在电视电影《还我清白》（{{lang|en|''My Son Is Innocent''}}，1996）中，标志着她转向剧情片。她还在电视电影《{{le|杀死我的老师|Killing_Mr._Griffin_(film)}}》（1997）中扮演了学生苏珊的极客小团体成员<ref name="Maytum"/>。

15岁时，为了不受[[童工|儿童劳动法]]影响，威廉斯在父母的同意下申请解除他们的监护权，以便能更好地追求演艺事业<ref name="mc127">{{citation |title=Belle Michelle |first=Leslie |last=Bennetts |work=Marie Claire |publisher=Hearst Corporation |page=127 |issue=08530 |date=February 2011 |accessdate=2011-07-08}}</ref>。因遭到严重的[[霸凌|霸凌]]，她在加州[[索拉纳海滩_(加利福尼亚州)|索拉纳海滩]]的{{le|圣达菲基督学校|Santa_Fe_Christian_Schools}}{{le|高级分部|Upper_school}}完成9年级后退学<ref name="schoolsnub">{{cite web |last=Peterson |first=Todd |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1169491,00.html |title=Michelle Williams Snubbed by Former School |work=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2006-03-03 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2011-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110329224056/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1169491,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，她在父亲的指导下[[在家自學|在家自學]]，从[[遙距教育|远程教育机构]]取得了[[普通教育發展證書|普通教育發展證書]]<ref name="thr2008"/>。

她搬到[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]，很快在青春剧《[[恋爱时代_(美国电视剧)|恋爱时代]]》中拿到了一个重要角色<ref name="mc127"/>。该剧是主创[[凯文·威廉姆森_(编剧)|凯文·威廉姆森]]半自传体剧集，故事基于他的早年生活。威廉斯日后说，她在当时认为自己从15岁起就懂得了她需明白的一切<ref name="wmag2010"/>。她于2011年表示自己选择脱离父母监管是受了其他年轻演员的影响<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/dailydish/detail?entry_id=80774#ixzz1RUzLt67F |title=Michelle Williams' emancipation prompted by Hollywood headlines |work=San Francisco Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Corporation |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2011-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916063229/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/dailydish/detail?entry_id=80774#ixzz1RUzLt67F |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1997年，威廉斯和几位演员朋友因不满得到的角色一起创作了一篇剧本，标题为《眨眼》（{{lang|en|''Blink''}}）。剧本被售出，但没有进一步发展<ref name="wonderland">{{cite web |url=http://www.wonderlandmagazine.com/features/michelle_ma_belle/ |title=Michelle Ma Belle |publisher=Wonderland Magazine |date=March 2008 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316183919/http://www.wonderlandmagazine.com/features/michelle_ma_belle/ |archivedate=2011-03-16 }}</ref>。

《恋爱时代》中的角色使威廉斯与其他几位主演[[詹姆斯·范德比克|詹姆斯·范德比克]]、[[姬蒂·荷姆絲|姬蒂·荷姆絲]]和[[約書亞·傑克遜|約書亞·傑克遜]]一起成名<ref name="peoplebio1"/>。她当时17岁，扮演{{le|简·林德利|Jen Lindley}}一角，为了拍摄剧集搬到[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]居住<ref name="vogue204">{{citation |title=A Field Guide to Getting Lost |page=204 |issue=08449 |first=Sally |last=Singer |work=[[Vogue_(magazine)|Vogue]] |publisher=Condé Nast Publications |date=October 2009 |accessdate=2011-07-06}}</ref>。她觉得自己和角色的相似之处是她们都成长得“太快了”，在《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的采访中，她将自己的角色描述为“这个稳重、无忧无虑的女孩也能与魔鬼搏斗”<ref name="peoplebio1"/>。她说出演《恋爱时代》使她能自己选择项目<ref name="wmag2010"/><ref name="dcreunion">{{cite web |url=http://tv.msn.com/tv/article.aspx?news=621773 |title=Michelle Williams open to 'Dawson's Creek' reunion |publisher=MSN |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2011-07-06 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113211800/http://tv.msn.com/tv/article.aspx?news=621773 |archive-date=2011-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，她还表示：
{{cquote|主演一部《恋爱时代》那样的剧那么久了……你花费很多时间去做一件你不完全投入的事情。当你把一年中的九个月用来做那样的工作，你得非常确定不要浪费剩下的宝贵的三个月。}}

威廉斯也继续出现在电影中。她的第一部主流作品是1998年的[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]《{{le|月光光心慌慌7|Halloween H20: 20 Years Later}}》<ref name="Maytum"/>。该片取得了商业成功，以1千7百万美元成本获得了5千5百万票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=halloween7.htm |title=Halloween: H20 |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb Inc]] |accessdate=2011-07-06 |archive-date=2011-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607134431/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=halloween7.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她与[[克里斯汀·邓斯特|克里斯汀·邓斯特]]共同主演了1999年的喜剧片《{{le|迪克 (1999年电影)|Dick (film)|迪克}}》。该片是对导致美国总统[[尼克松|尼克松]]辞职的[[水门事件|水门事件]]的[[戲仿|戲仿]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/library/film/080499dick-film-review.html |title='Dick': That Gap in the Nixon Tapes? Maybe a Teen-Age Cry of Love |last=Holden |first=Stephen |date=1999-08-04 |work=The New York Times |publisher=[[The_New_York_Times_Company|The New York Times Company]] |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2014-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906125518/http://www.nytimes.com/library/film/080499dick-film-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她开始接拍更有挑战性的影片<ref name="movieline">{{cite web |url=http://www.movieline.com/2011/02/could-blake-lively-be-the-next-michelle-williams.php |first=Chris |last=Spargo |title=Could Blake Lively Be The Next Michelle Williams? |work=[[Movieline|Movieline]] |publisher=[[Mail.com_Media|Mail.com Media]] |date=2011-02-19 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110223093325/http://www.movieline.com/2011/02/could-blake-lively-be-the-next-michelle-williams.php |archivedate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> ，在女同性恋题材电影《[[戀戀模範生|戀戀模範生]]》（1999）中出演一个小角色，该片由{{le|潔米·巴比特|Jamie Babbit}}导演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/but-i-m-a-cheerleader-1999 |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=But I'm a Cheerleader (1999) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2011-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808150844/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/but-i-m-a-cheerleader-1999 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===== 期货交易 =====
1997年，威廉斯跟随父亲的脚步，参加罗宾斯世界冠军杯期货交易竞赛（{{lang|en|Robbins World Cup Championship of Futures Trading}}），用起始的1万美元获得了超过10万美元，赢得了该项赛事。凭借900%的获利率，她成为了该赛事自1984年首次举行后排名第3高的冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.robbinstrading.com/world_cup_championship/|title=Robbins Trading, World Cup Advisors, World Cup Championship  - Robbins Trading Co.|publisher=Robbins Trading Co.|language=en|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130802073228/http://www.robbinstrading.com/world_cup_championship/|archive-date=2013-08-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/michelle-williams-trader-father-2011-1?op=1|title=Here's How Actress Michelle Williams Won The World Cup Of Futures Trading Award At Age 17|date=2011-01-26|work=Business Insider|language=en|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2013-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516180047/http://www.businessinsider.com/michelle-williams-trader-father-2011-1?op=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2000年-2005年 ====
2000年，她出演了{{lang|en|[[HBO|HBO]]}}电视电影系列《{{le|如果墙会说话2|If These Walls Could Talk 2}}》。这个系列有三个部分，分别讲述了女同性恋情侣在同一地点不同时期的故事。威廉斯和[[科洛·塞维尼|科洛·塞维尼]]出现在第二部中，表现了1972年[[女权运动|女权运动]]中苦涩的分-{}-裂。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》影评人肯·塔克（{{lang|en|Ken Tucker}}）赞扬了塞维尼的表现，但认为威廉斯“努力咧嘴笑以显得顽皮”，把角色演的过火了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,275597,00.html |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner Inc |title=If These Walls Could Talk 2 (2000) |first=Ken |last=Tucker |date=2000-03-03 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |language=en |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112120040/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,275597,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

从这时起，威廉斯开始参与观众群较小的[[獨立電影|獨立電影]]。“我感觉自己没有用一种特别闪耀、引人注目的方式工作”，她对《[[时尚_(杂志)|时尚]]》杂志说，“如果你不特意去寻找它们，你会错过那些我参演的令我感到自豪的电影。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"I feel like I haven't been working in a particularly flashy or visible way," she reflected to Vogue magazine. "If you weren't looking for them, you would miss the movies that I've made that I'm proud of."}}|group="原文"}}<ref name="peoplebio1"/>”她和{{le|安娜·弗里尔|Anna Friel}}共同主演了2001年影片《{{link-en|没有你的我 (2001年电影)|Me_Without_You_(film)|没有你的我}}》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9D0DE7DA1331F936A35754C0A9649C8B63&partner=Rotten%20Tomatoes |title=Film Review; Best Friends Who Are Also Worst Enemies Struggle in a Web of Emotions |first=Stephen |last=Holden |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2002-07-05 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |language=en |archive-date=2012-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217153822/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9D0DE7DA1331F936A35754C0A9649C8B63&partner=Rotten%20Tomatoes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该片收获的评价褒贬不一，[[爛番茄|爛番茄网站]]上的65篇影评得出的新鲜度为66%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/me_without_you/ |title=Me Without You (2001) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] |accessdate=2011-07-07 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406123133/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/me_without_you |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的下一部作品是2000年的《{{le|我的忧郁青春|Prozac Nation (film)}}》，该片由[[姬絲汀娜·莉芝|姬絲汀娜·莉芝]]主演，改编自{{le|伊丽莎白·伍尔茨|Elizabeth Wurtzel}}的同名自传，讲述了与[[重性抑郁障碍|重性抑郁障碍]]作斗争的经历<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reelviews.net/movies/p/prozac_nation.html |title=Prozac Nation |work=Reel Reviews |first=James |last=Berardinelli |date=2003-03-11 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |language=en |archive-date=2011-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111221044854/http://www.reelviews.net/movies/p/prozac_nation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。被问及扮演女主角的室友是否有趣，威廉斯说：“我认为这个角色需要帮助女主角。一个像这样（用拳拍击她的手）站立的人，让女主角能坚持和抑郁症搏斗。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"I think what it needed to be was helpful. Somebody to stand like this [punches her hand] so that she [Ricci] could keep smacking up against it."}}|group="原文"}}”

下一年，她在《{{le|利蓝的美国|The United States of Leland}}》（2003）中扮演一位被谋杀男孩的姐妹<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20040402/REVIEWS/404020302/1023 |title=The United States of Leland |first=Roger |last=Ebert |authorlink=Roger Ebert |publisher=[[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]] |date=2004-04-02 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |language=en |archive-date=2012-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013011858/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20040402%2FREVIEWS%2F404020302%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片所获评价不佳，《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的连姆·蕾西（{{lang|en|Liam Lacey}}）称其“既没有深刻见解，也没有精良制作{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"neither an insightful nor well-made film."}}|group="原文"}}<ref>{{cite news |title=Review: The United States of Leland |work=Globe and Mail |publisher=Phillip Crawley |first=Liam |last=Lacey |date=2004-04-09 |accessdate=2011-07-07|language=en}}</ref>”。同年，威廉斯参演了喜剧剧情片《[[下一站，幸福_(電影)|下一站，幸福]]》。片中男主角是个住在废弃火车库房的侏儒（[[彼特·丁拉基|彼特·丁拉基]]饰演），与威廉斯饰演的图书管理员发展出了一段友谊。其他参演的明星有[[鲍比·坎纳瓦尔|鲍比·坎纳瓦尔]]和[[派翠西娅·克拉克森|派翠西娅·克拉克森]]，全体演员获得了[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]最佳群戏的提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20040116&slug=sag16 |title='Mystic River,' 'Station Agent' top SAG award nominations |work=[[The_Seattle_Times|The Seattle Times]] |publisher=[[The_Seattle_Times_Company|The Seattle Times Company]] |date=2004-01-16 |accessdate=2011-07-09 |language=en |archive-date=2012-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120128175258/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20040116&slug=sag16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

电视剧《恋爱时代》于2003年完结后，威廉斯承认难以找到合适的角色，她说自己被视为一个“流行一时的年轻美女”（{{lang|en|pop tart}}）<ref name="dcreunion"/>。她在{{le|威廉斯顿戏剧节|Williamstown Theatre Festival}}上参演了[[契诃夫|契诃夫]]的舞台剧《[[櫻桃園|櫻桃園]]》，与{{le|琳达·伊蒙|Linda Emond}}和[[杰西卡·查斯坦|杰西卡·查斯坦]]合作<ref>{{cite web|title=The Cherry Orchard|url=http://wtfestival.org/performance?PerformanceID=77|accessdate=2012-08-08|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603135110/http://wtfestival.org/performance?PerformanceID=77|archivedate=2013-06-03}}</ref>。

[[溫·韋德斯|溫·韋德斯]]在创作《{{le|迷失天使城|Land of Plenty}}》（2004）剧本时把威廉斯预想为其中的角色，该片探寻了美国在后911时代的焦虑和理想的幻灭<ref name="nytimes08">{{cite web |first=Dennis |last=Lim |title=For Michelle Williams, It's All Personal: Filmmakers Love Her Work, While the Public Remembers Her Heath Ledger Connection |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/07/movies/moviesspecial/07lim.html?pagewanted=2 |date=2008-09-07 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308163016/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/07/movies/moviesspecial/07lim.html?pagewanted=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。威廉斯在其中扮演流浪汉收容所的工作人员拉娜（{{lang|en|Lana}}），试图与越战老兵舅舅取得联系<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2005/10/12/movies/12plen.html |title=A Desire to Heal the Rifts in a Troubled Landscape |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2005-10-12 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2013-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622034034/http://movies.nytimes.com/2005/10/12/movies/12plen.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她获得了2006年[[獨立精神獎|獨立精神獎]]最佳女主角的提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/entertainment/shutterisland/7293427/Michelle-Williams-biography-Shutter-Island.html |title=Michelle Williams biography: Shutter Island |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |date=2010-02-23 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125194644/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/entertainment/shutterisland/7293427/Michelle-Williams-biography-Shutter-Island.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，她出现在影片《{{le|假想英雄|Imaginary Heroes}}》（2005）中，剧情围绕儿子自尽对一个郊区家庭的影响<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2005/02/25/DDGLRBFT691.DTL |title=Details etch a portrait of family grief over suicide |work=San Francisco Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Corporation |first=Mick |last=LaSalle |date=2005-02-25 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2005-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050314011542/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2005%2F02%2F25%2FDDGLRBFT691.DTL |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该片的全球票房收入不到30万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=imaginaryheroes.htm |title=Imaginary Heroes |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-08 |language=en |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629221737/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=imaginaryheroes.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她与歌手[[米特·洛夫|米特·洛夫]]共同主演了年代片《[[一杆进洞|一杆进洞]]》，它是导演{{le|理查德·莱德斯|Richard Ledes}}的首部剧情长篇，没有引起多少关注<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/06/movies/06hole.html?ex=1146974400&en=23c332de43a9e095&ei=5083&partner=Rotten%20Tomatoes |title=Debating the Benefits of a Transorbital Lobotomy |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |first=Dana |last=Stevens |date=2005-05-06 |accessdate=2011-07-08|language=en}}</ref>。

威廉斯少见地出现在喜剧片中，参演了{{le|迈克尔·修华特|Michael Showalter}}自编自导自演的《{{le|巴克斯特|The Baxter}}》（2005）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-baxter-2005#content |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=The Baxter (2005) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-09 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111054446/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-baxter-2005#content |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10005403-the_baxter/ |title=The Baxter (2005) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2011-07-09 |language=en |archive-date=2011-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110918162407/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10005403-the_baxter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这部电影的大多数评价为负面，但威廉斯收获了赞扬。

威廉斯在2005年影片《[[断背山|断背山]]》中的表现赢得了大众的认可。该片由[[李安|李安]]导演，讲述了{{le|埃尼斯·德·玛尔|Ennis Del Mar}}和{{le|杰克·特威斯特|Jack Twist}}之间的同性爱情（两角色分别由[[希斯·萊傑|希斯·萊傑]]和[[杰克·吉林哈尔|杰克·吉林哈尔]]扮演）<ref>{{cite book|last1=Proulx |first1=Annie |last2=McMurtry |first2=Larry |last3=Ossana |first3=Diana |year=2005, 2006|title=Brokeback Mountain: Story to Screenplay|url=https://archive.org/details/brokebackmountai00anni_0 |publisher=London, New York, Toronto and Sydney: Harper Perennial|isbn=978-0-00-723430-1|language=en}}</ref>。威廉斯扮演了埃尼斯的妻子阿尔玛（{{lang|en|Alma}}），在片中目睹两位男主角的拥抱后意识到他们之间关系的真相。选角导演{{le|艾薇·考夫曼|Avy Kaufman}}在观看了《下一站，幸福》后建议李安让威廉斯出演阿尔玛<ref name="almacasting">{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1146101,00.html |title=Even Cowboy's Wives Get the Blues |first=Karen |last=Valby |date=2006-01-06 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner Inc |accessdate=2011-07-10 |language=en |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112123050/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1146101,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这部电影成为了票房大热门，以1千4百万美元成本在全球席卷1亿7千8百万美元票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=brokebackmountain.htm |title=Brokeback Mountain |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-10 |language=en |archive-date=2011-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603100814/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=brokebackmountain.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它也以8项提名领跑[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|第78届奥斯卡金像奖]]，包括威廉斯的[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角奖]]提名。该片最终赢得了3项奥斯卡奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/ref/movies/redcarpet/2006oscars.html |title=List of Academy Award Winners and Nominees |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |year=2006 |accessdate=2011-07-10 |language=en |archive-date=2018-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124191459/http://www.nytimes.com/ref/movies/redcarpet/2006oscars.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。威廉斯在出席颁奖典礼时穿的{{le|橙黄色王薇薇礼服裙|Saffron Vera Wang dress of Michelle Williams}}被《[[柯夢波丹|柯夢波丹]]》杂志称赞为史上最佳奥斯卡礼服之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/celebrity/red-carpet-dresses/best-and-worst-oscar-style|title=Oscars Best and Worst Dressed|work=[[Cosmopolitan_(magazine)|Cosmopolitan]]|accessdate=2011-05-24|language=en|archive-date=2011-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110602140036/http://www.cosmopolitan.com/celebrity/red-carpet-dresses/best-and-worst-oscar-style|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2006年至今 ====
威廉斯在产子后以《{{le|雄鹰垂危|The Hawk Is Dying}}》（2006）一片回归。该片讲述了乔治（[[保罗·吉亚玛提|保罗·吉亚玛提]]饰）为试图寻找人生意义训练了一只野生[[红尾鵟|红尾鵟]]。威廉斯扮演了乔治外甥弗雷德（[[邁克爾·皮特|邁克爾·皮特]]饰）的女友，是唯一理解乔治愈发沉迷其中的人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-hawk-is-dying-2006#content |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=The Hawk Is Dying (2006) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216003131/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-hawk-is-dying-2006#content |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这部电影在美国国内仅在一家影院上映，入账7,000美元票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hawkisdying.htm |title=The Hawk Is Dying |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-04 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616020646/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hawkisdying.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在完成生产的5个月后，威廉斯回到《{{le|最炎热的国度|The Hottest State}}》（2006）的摄影机前。该片由[[伊森·霍克|伊森·霍克]]改编自他1996年出版的小说<ref>{{citation |title=A Star Is Born |first=Graham |last=Fuller |authorlink=Graham Fuller |work=Interview |page=166 |publisher=Brant Publications |date=March 2006 |accessdate=2011-07-04|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-hottest-state-2006#content |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=The Hottest State (2006) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216003117/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/the-hottest-state-2006#content |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影评人给予了负面评价，觉得它过于自我沉迷。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》杂志的莱斯利·菲尔普林（{{lang|en|Leslie Felperin}}）认为让威廉斯扮演主人公的前女友之一是大材小用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117931449?refcatid=31 |title=The Hottest State |first=Leslie |last=Felperin |work=Variety |publisher=[[Reed_Business_Information|Reed Business Information]] |date=2006-09-02 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2011-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524025255/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117931449?refcatid=31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片于8月24日开始了小范围的公映，最终的票房成绩为137,340美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hotteststate.htm |title=The Hottest State |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609132651/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hotteststate.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

威廉斯在[[鲍勃·迪伦|鲍勃·迪伦]]的传记片《[[搖滾啟示錄|搖滾啟示錄]]》中出演了[[安迪·沃荷|安迪·沃荷]]的缪斯女神[[伊迪·塞奇威克|伊迪·塞奇威克]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/i-m-not-there-2007-4 |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=I'm Not There (2007) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216003105/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/i-m-not-there-2007-4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年10月，她签约影片《{{le|玩叛游戏|Deception (2008 film)}}》（2008），饰演一位勾引[[伊万·迈克格雷戈|伊万·迈克格雷戈]]角色的金发女郎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/feed.asp?NID=19642 |title=Michelle Williams Seduces The Tourist |work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |publisher=Bauer Consumer Media |date=2006-10-03 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020182809/http://www.empireonline.com/news/feed.asp?NID=19642 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。威廉斯和迈克格雷戈在同年上映的《{{le|燃烧弹 (2008年电影)|Incendiary (film)|燃烧弹}}》中再次合作，该片有关恐怖袭击后发生的余波，改编自{{le|克里斯·克利夫|Chris Cleave}}2005年的同名小说<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3562319/Incendiary-from-calorie-counting-with-Bridget-Jones-to-terror-in-the-streets.html |title=Incendiary: from calorie-counting with Bridget Jones to terror in the streets |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |first=Sheila |last=Johnston |date=2008-10-20 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201025628/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3562319/Incendiary-from-calorie-counting-with-Bridget-Jones-to-terror-in-the-streets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在片中扮演了主人公，一位有婚外情的英国母亲，在袭击中失去了丈夫和儿子。《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的罗伯特·汉克斯（{{lang|en|Robert Hanks}}）评论该片“草率”，认为威廉斯值得更好的电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/incendiary-15-971242.html |first=Robert |last=Hanks |title=Incendiary (15) |work=The Independent |publisher=Independent Print Limited |date=2008-10-24 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2010-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100315175256/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/incendiary-15-971242.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

随后，编剧[[查理·卡夫曼|查理·卡夫曼]]因欣赏威廉斯在《迪克》中的表现让她参演自己的导演处女作《{{le|纽约提喻法|Synecdoche, New York}}》（2008），其他演员有[[菲臘·西摩·荷夫曼|菲臘·西摩·荷夫曼]]和[[艾米莉·沃森|艾米莉·沃森]]<ref name="nytimes08"/>。该片成为了一个[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]，但受到了媒体称赞，出现在许多影评人的年度十佳名单中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=synecdochenewyork.htm |title=Synecdoche, New York |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2011-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815172319/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=synecdochenewyork.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=2008 Top Ten List |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2011-07-05|language=en}}</ref>。威廉斯主演了小成本制作的低调剧情片《{{le|温迪和露西|Wendy and Lucy}}》，由[[凯莉·雷查德|凯莉·雷查德]]执导，讲述了居无定所的温迪在经历了一系列挫折后寻找她的爱犬露西，试图开始新生活的故事<ref name="wandl">{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/09/us-wendyandlucy-idUSTRE4B83K320081209 |title=Michelle Williams says "Wendy and Lucy" role a gift |first=Michelle |last=Nicholas |publisher=[[Thomson_Reuters|Thomson Reuters]] |date=2008-12-09 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140452/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/09/us-wendyandlucy-idUSTRE4B83K320081209 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wendylucy1"/>。威廉斯与其他人（包括导演）的观点不同，她不觉得该片令人沮丧，说：“我个人喜欢看这种类型的电影，感到了安慰，因为它们减轻了我的孤独。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"Personally I like seeing those kinds of movies. I find them comforting because they make me feel less alone."}}|group="原文"}}”作为《温迪与露西》的女主演，威廉斯也喜欢影片的纪实风格<ref name="wandl"/>。《[[休斯敦纪事报|休斯敦纪事报]]》的艾米·布兰科尔（{{lang|en|Amy Blancolll}}）说她的表演是全片的关键，是“一项举足轻重的成就{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"a bare-bones accomplishment of no small heft"}}|group="原文"}}”<ref name="wendylucy1">{{cite web |url=http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ent/movies/reviews/6271666.html#ixzz1RHlvxtq3 |title=Wendy and Lucy is a low-key treasure of a film |first=Amy |last=Blancolll |work=Houston Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Corporation |date=2008-02-19 |accessdate=2011-07-05|language=en}}</ref>。[[多伦多影评人协会|多伦多影评人协会]]授予了威廉斯最佳女主角奖，也将该电影选为最佳影片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/film/story/2008/12/16/tfca-best-list.html |title=Toronto critics name indie drama Wendy and Lucy best of 2008 |work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2008-12-16 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2012-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109224424/http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/film/story/2008/12/16/tfca-best-list.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年影片《{{le|猛犸象 (电影)|Mammoth (2009 film)|猛犸象}}》让威廉斯到[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[泰国|泰国]]和[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]拍摄<ref name="mamoth1">{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/27/people-williams-dc-idUSN2638529920071027 |title=Michelle Williams joins "Mammoth" family drama |first=Stuart |last=Kemp |publisher=Thomson Reuters |date=2007-10-26 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924123718/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/27/people-williams-dc-idUSN2638529920071027 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她和[[蓋爾·賈西亞·貝納|蓋爾·賈西亞·貝納]]演了一对面临[[全球化|全球化]]生活挑战的夫妻。该片是瑞典导演[[卢卡斯·穆迪森|卢卡斯·穆迪森]]的第一部英语电影<ref name="mamoth1"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mammoth.htm |title=Mammoth |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2011-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726124336/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mammoth.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

