威廉斯在[[马丁·斯科塞斯|马丁·斯科塞斯]]执导的《[[隔離島|隔離島]]》中出演女配角，一位出没在男主角（[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]饰）梦中的已逝妻子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/shutter-island-2010-1#content |work=Total Film |publisher=Future Publishing |title=Shutter Island (2010) |first=Matt |last=Maytum |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2011-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110417143047/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/the-evolution-of-michelle-williams/shutter-island-2010-1#content |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这部心理惊悚片改编自[[丹尼斯·勒翰|丹尼斯·勒翰]]2003年的同名畅销小说。它原定于2009年10月首映，但推迟至2010年2月19日才上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/02/22/shutter-islands-release-date-magic/ |title='Shutter Island': A release date change proves a stroke of marketing magic |first=Owen |last=Gleiberman |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111060844/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/02/22/shutter-islands-release-date-magic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该片在超过2,900家影院收入了4110百万美元，成为了威廉斯作品中发行规模最大、首映周末成绩最佳的影片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=michellewilliams.htm |title=Michelle Williams |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb Inc |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616195756/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=michellewilliams.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月，她在浪漫剧情片《[[藍色情人節|藍色情人節]]》中与高斯林一起饰演一对婚姻出现问题的夫妻。编剧兼导演{{le|德里克·斯安弗朗斯|Derek Cianfrance}}让两人在一个月中的白天住在一起，以便进入角色<ref>{{cite news |title=The New Star Power |work=Newsweek |publisher=The Newsweek Daily Beast Company |first1=David |last1=Ansen |first2=Ramin |last2=Setoodeh |date=2011-01-23 |accessdate=2011-07-05|language=en}}</ref>。威廉斯日后说这段经历很棒，希望自己在当时能更加享受这一过程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2010/12/03/michelle_williams_talks_blue_valentine_meeks_cutoff_playing_marilyn_monroe1/ |title=Michelle Williams Talks Blue Valentine, Meek's Cutoff Playing Marilyn Monroe, Female Directors |first=Anne |last=Thompson |work=indieWIRE |publisher=SnagFilms |date=2010-12-03 |accessdate=2011-07-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807113214/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2010/12/03/michelle_williams_talks_blue_valentine_meeks_cutoff_playing_marilyn_monroe1/ |archivedate=2011-08-07 }}</ref>。该片在2010年的[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]、[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]和[[倫敦影展|倫敦影展]]上放映，受到了影评人的青睐<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/05/cannes-blue-valentine-another-year-mike-leigh.html |title=Cannes 2010: The Euros love 'Blue Valentine' like Nutella; Sony Classics makes this not just another year |first=Steven |last=Zeitchik |work=The Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2010-05-18 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410234511/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/05/cannes-blue-valentine-another-year-mike-leigh.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/honor_roll_2010_blue_valentine_director_derek_cianfrance/ |title=Honor Roll 2010: "Blue Valentine" Director Derek Cianfrance |first=Peter |last=Knegt |work=indieWIRE |publisher=Snagfilms |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2016-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529182242/http://www.indiewire.com/article/honor_roll_2010_blue_valentine_director_derek_cianfrance |dead-url=no }}</ref>。两位演员都收获了赞扬以及多个奖项的注意<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/01/07/MVK31GPNCQ.DTL |title=Blue Valentine |work=San Francisco Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Corporation |first=Mick |last=LaSalle |date=2011-01-07 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324122738/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F01%2F07%2FMVK31GPNCQ.DTL |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20453723,00.html |title=Blue Valentine (2010) |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2011-01-06 |first=Owen |last=Gleiberman |accessdate=2011-07-05 |language=en |archive-date=2012-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120011655/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20453723%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。威廉斯获得了[[金球奖_(影视奖项)|金球奖]]和[[奥斯卡奖|奥斯卡奖]]的最佳女主角提名。

西部片《{{le|米克的近路|Meek's Cutoff}}》是威廉斯和导演雷查德的再次合作，拍摄于[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[柏恩斯_(俄勒岡州)|柏恩斯]]。该片基于1845年发生在[[奧勒岡小徑|奧勒岡小徑]]上的历史事件改编，讲述了西部向导{{le|史蒂芬·米克|Stephen Meek}}带领大篷车队伍穿越一片沙漠的险恶旅程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2011/05/25/20110525meeks-cutoff-movie-review-goodykoontz.html |title='Meek's Cutoff,' 4 stars |first=Bill |last=Goodykoontz |work=Arizona Republic |publisher=Gannett Company |date=2011-05-26 |accessdate=2011-07-04|language=en}}</ref>。这部阴郁的年代电影在[[第67届威尼斯国际电影节|第67届威尼斯国际电影节]]上首映后受到良好反响，于2011年4月8日开始了小规模公映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2010/sep/06/meeks-cutoff-post-mortem-venice |title=Meek's Cutoff and Post Mortem shine at Venice film festival |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian News and Media Limited |date=2010-09-06 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2012-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305180936/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2010/sep/06/meeks-cutoff-post-mortem-venice |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.movieline.com/2011/03/michelle-williams-on-meeks-cutoff-goodbyes-and-getting-lost-at-the-movies.php?page=all |title=Michelle Williams on Meek's Cutoff, Goodbyes and Getting Lost At the Movies |first=S.T. |last=Vanairsdale |work=Movieline |publisher=Mail.com Media |date=2011-03-30 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407031418/http://www.movieline.com/2011/03/michelle-williams-on-meeks-cutoff-goodbyes-and-getting-lost-at-the-movies.php?page=all |archivedate=2011-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

威廉斯在2011年英国剧情片《[[与梦露的一周|与梦露的一周]]》中赢得了扮演[[玛丽莲·梦露|玛丽莲·梦露]]的机会，其他候选人有[[姬·韓遜|姬·韓遜]]、[[斯嘉丽·约翰逊|斯嘉丽·约翰逊]]和[[艾米·亚当斯|艾米·亚当斯]]。该片改编自{{le|科林·克拉克|Colin Clark (filmmaker)}}的两本小说，描述了1957年影片《{{le|游龙戏凤 (1957年电影)|The Prince and the Showgirl|游龙戏凤}}》的摄制过程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a168717/johansson-in-lead-to-play-marilyn-monroe.html|title=Johansson 'in lead to play Marilyn Monroe|last=Minaya|first=Marcel l|date=2009-08-01|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|publisher=[[Hachette_Filipacchi_Médias|Hachette Filipacchi (UK) Ltd]]|accessdate=2011-07-04|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924015521/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a168717/johansson-in-lead-to-play-marilyn-monroe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.trendrabbit.com/2011/11/michelle-williams-transforms-into-hollywoods-biggest-starlet-my-week-with-marilyn/ |title=Michelle Williams Transforms Into Hollywood's Biggest Starlet |work=Trendrabbit |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420032904/http://www.trendrabbit.com/2011/11/michelle-williams-transforms-into-hollywoods-biggest-starlet-my-week-with-marilyn/ |archivedate=2012-04-20 |access-date=2015-05-17 }}</ref>。威廉斯一开始害怕接下这个角色，拒绝了邀请。她解释道：“无论是外形还是声音，她的一切都和我不同。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"Physically and vocally, everything about her is different from me"}}|group="原文"}}”最终，她觉得这个机会太好了，不应放弃<ref>{{cite web |url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/11/26/michelle-williams-was-terrified-to-play-marilyn-monroe/ |title=Michelle Williams was terrified to play Marilyn Monroe |first=Mark |last=Marino |work=CNN |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2010-11-26 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325033539/https://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/11/26/michelle-williams-was-terrified-to-play-marilyn-monroe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。威廉斯为了片中的唱歌部分上了声乐课程，因为假唱不自在<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2012/01/22/newsweek-s-oscar-roundtable-reveals-actors-private-parts.html |title=14th Oscar Roundtable |publisher=The Newsweek Daily Beast Company |work=Newsweek |date=2011-01-23 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123091332/http://www.thedailybeast.com/newsweek/2012/01/22/newsweek-s-oscar-roundtable-reveals-actors-private-parts.html |archive-date=2012-01-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她凭此片赢得了[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角|金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角奖]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Chen|first=Joyce|title=Golden Globes winner Michelle Williams: I'm inspired by my daughter's 'bravery and exuberance'|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/michelle-williams-thanks-daughter-matilda-golden-globes-win-article-1.1006965?localLinksEnabled=false|work=NY Daily News|accessdate=2012-01-16|date=2012-01-16|language=en|archive-date=2013-07-16|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I8yXoQCa?url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/michelle-williams-thanks-daughter-matilda-golden-globes-win-article-1.1006965?localLinksEnabled=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威廉斯在下一部作品《{{le|跳支华尔兹|Take This Waltz (film)}}》中与[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]一起扮演一对年轻夫妻，该片由[[莎拉·波莉|莎拉·波莉]]执导，摄于加拿大，探讨了一夫一妻制和婚姻中的忠诚问题<ref name="wmag2010">{{citation |title=Heart to Heart |first=Lynn |last=Hirschberg |issue=08453 |page=142 |work=[[W_(magazine)|W]] |publisher=[[Conde_Nast_Publications|Conde Nast Publications]] |date=October 2010 |accessdate=2011-06-29|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/archives/new_images_seth_rogen_michelle_williams_in_sarah_polleys_take_this_waltz/ |title=New Look: Seth Rogen & Michelle Williams In Sarah Polley's 'Take This Waltz' |work=IndieWIRE |publisher=Snagfilms |first=Edward |last=Davis |date=2011-05-17 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623234718/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/archives/new_images_seth_rogen_michelle_williams_in_sarah_polleys_take_this_waltz |archivedate=2011-06-23 }}</ref>。威廉斯和[[詹姆斯·法蘭科|詹姆斯·法蘭科]]共同主演了[[迪士尼|华特迪士尼影片]]的{{lang|en|3D}}前传片《[[魔境仙踪|魔境仙踪]]》，该片发行于2013年3月8日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-sets-oz-great-powerful-192298 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |title=Disney Sets 'Oz, the Great and Powerful' for 2013 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2011-05-25 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223045704/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-sets-oz-great-powerful-192298 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她还签约出演该片的续作<ref name="signed-sequel">{{cite web |url=http://www.fandango.com/movieblog/chatter-who-should-replace-sam-raimi-as-director-of-oz-sequel-736024.html |title=Chatter: Who Should Replace Sam Raimi as Director of the Oz Sequel? |publisher=Fandango.com |date=2013-03-11 |language=en |access-date=2015-05-17 |archive-date=2013-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130315114715/http://www.fandango.com/movieblog/chatter-who-should-replace-sam-raimi-as-director-of-oz-sequel-736024.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="notraimi">{{cite web |url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/cast-signed-for-oz-the-great-powerful-sequel-but-not-sam-raimi |title=Cast Signed for 'Oz: The Great & Powerful' Sequel But Not Sam Raimi |publisher=firstshowing.net |date=2013-03-11 |language=en |access-date=2015-05-17 |archive-date=2013-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314021949/http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/cast-signed-for-oz-the-great-powerful-sequel-but-not-sam-raimi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年7月，她成为了[[路易·威登|路易·威登]]手提包的新代言人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.eonline.com/news/442180/michelle-williams-rocks-sultry-red-lips-as-new-face-of-louis-vuitton-see-the-pics|title=E! Online Louis Vuitton article|date=2013-07-24|work=E! Online|language=en|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2013-07-26|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130726094436/http://au.eonline.com/news/442180/michelle-williams-rocks-sultry-red-lips-as-new-face-of-louis-vuitton-see-the-pics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

威廉斯在音乐剧《[[歌厅_(音乐剧)|歌厅]]》重排版中扮演歌女{{le|萨利·鲍尔斯|Sally Bowles}}一角，首次亮相[[百老汇|百老汇]]舞台。这一版于2014年4月24日开演，她于2014年11月9日结束自己的任期<ref>{{cite web|last=Stasio|first=Marilyn|title=‘Cabaret’ Starring Michelle Williams and Alan Cumming|url=http://variety.com/2014/legit/reviews/broadway-review-cabaret-starring-michelle-williams-and-alan-cumming-1201163155/|publisher=Variety Media|language=en|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808190235/https://variety.com/2014/legit/reviews/broadway-review-cabaret-starring-michelle-williams-and-alan-cumming-1201163155/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，威廉斯主演了二战背景的爱情片《[[法国战恋曲|法国战恋曲]]》，改编自同名小说。她扮演了一位爱上德国士兵的法国村女<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/the-weinstein-co-suite-francaise-margot-robbie-ruth-wilson-laura-michelle-williams-shooting-starts-brussels-paris/|title=Margot Robbie, Ruth Wilson, Alexandra Maria Lara Join Weinstein Co.'s 'Suite Française'|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|date=2013-06-27|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher=[[PMC_(company)|Penske Media Corporation]]|accessdate=2013-07-08|language=en|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330040935/http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/the-weinstein-co-suite-francaise-margot-robbie-ruth-wilson-laura-michelle-williams-shooting-starts-brussels-paris/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
[[File:Michelle_Williams3_Berlinale_2010.jpg|thumb]]上《[[禁闭岛|禁闭岛]]》的首映礼。]]
2004年，威廉斯和[[希斯·萊傑|希斯·萊傑]]在他们共同参演的《断背山》片场相遇后开始约会<ref name="center">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20158581,00.html |first=Courtney |last=Rubin |title=Michelle Williams: 'Daughter Is Center of My Life' |work=People |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2007-11-06 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2013-01-20 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dp0wgw0D?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20158581,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/2011-01-06/gossip/27086710_1_untimely-death-nightline-ledger-and-williams|title=Michelle Williams slams 'Nightline' over 'devastating' interview about Heath Ledger's death|first=Joyce|last=Chen|work=New York Daily News|date=2011-01-06|accessdate=2011-07-11|language=en|archive-date=2012-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310124120/http://articles.nydailynews.com/2011-01-06/gossip/27086710_1_untimely-death-nightline-ledger-and-williams|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年4月末，《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》杂志首先报道了两人将会有孩子的消息。同年，威廉斯生下他们的女儿玛蒂尔达·罗斯·萊傑（{{lang|en|Matilda Rose Ledger}}）<ref name="peoplebio1"/>。他们在恋爱期间一起居住在纽约[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]<ref name="almacasting"/>。到2007年9月，这对情侣已和平分手，结束了三年的恋情<ref name="split">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20054428,00.html |title=Heath Ledger and Michelle Williams Split |work=People |publisher=Time Warner Inc |first=Charlotte |last=Triggs |date=2007-09-02 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2011-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910022418/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20054428,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。关于分手，《人物》引用了威廉斯告诉《{{lang|en|[[ELLE|ELLE]]}}》杂志的话：“我不知道去哪里。我不能想象世界上有任何地方能给我好心情。{{#tag:ref|原文：{{lang|en|"I didn't know where to go. I couldn't imagine any place in the world that was gonna feel good to me."}}|group="原文"}}<ref name="peoplebio1"/>”萊傑于2008年因药物过量突然去世后，常处于镁光灯下的母女二人成为了媒体和[[狗仔队|狗仔队]]的追逐对象<ref name="vogue204"/><ref name="nytimes08"/>。因此，威廉斯在2009年底前很少接受采访<ref name="vogue205">{{citation |title=A Field Guide to Getting Lost |page=205 |issue=08449 |first=Sally |last=Singer |work=Vogue |publisher=Condé Nast Publications |date=October 2009 |accessdate=2011-07-11|language=en}}</ref>。

2008年2月1日，威廉斯在萊傑死后第一次发表了公开声明<ref>{{cite web |title=Michelle Williams Breaks Silence on Heath's Death |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20175486,00.html |work=People |publisher=Time Warner Inc |date=2008-02-01 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2011-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110329101700/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20175486,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她表达了自己的悲痛，表示萊傑的精神会在长得像他的女儿身上长存。同月晚些时候，她出席了他的纪念仪式和葬礼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1581264/heath-ledger-remembered-at-funeral-australia.jhtml |title=Heath Ledger Remembered At Funeral; Michelle Williams Takes A Tearful Ocean Swim In His Honor |publisher=[[Viacom|Viacom]] |first=Jem |last=Aswad |date=2008-02-09 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2012-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615183715/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1581264/heath-ledger-remembered-at-funeral-australia.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

